		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>NES 2.0 Additions Proposal</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I would like to propose additions to the NES 2.0 format for your esteemed consideration. Reasons:<ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>I have counted at least ten games now that require Dendy timing and are incompatible with RP2C02 and RP2C07 timing. &quot;Incompatible&quot; in one case means the game (西天取经 II - Journey to the West) crashes at the beginning of a boss battle.</li><li>Several mutually-incompatible Famiclones need to be distinguished from each other.</li><li>The Vs. Dual System is not supported.</li><li>Additional protection types on the Vs. Unisystem need to be specified.</li></ol><br />Edit: Updated version <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=17213&amp;p=220624#p220624" class="postlink">here</a>.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


