		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><strong>NTSC Famiclones:</strong><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">UMC UA6527 (CPU)<br />UMC UA6528 (PPU)</div><br /><strong>PAL Famiclones</strong> (&quot;dendy-timing&quot;)<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">MicroGenius MG-P-501 (CPU) <br />MicroGenius MG-P-502 (PPU)<br />UMC UA6527P (CPU)<br />UMC UA6538 (PPU)<br />TA-03NP1 6527P (CPU)<br />TA-02NP 6538 (PPU)<br />HA6527P (CPU)<br />HA6538 (PPU)<br />UMC UM6561 series (NOAC)</div><br />And <a href="http://forum.pegasus-gry.com/index.php?PHPSESSID=u4ft15rr4nj12d6hqkpbhbebr5&amp;topic=2315.msg27570#msg27570" class="postlink">lots of them...</a><br />BTW, i don't know any famiclone which have Real PAL NES timing.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
